## Distances exposées

| Symbole | Espace | Type | Bornes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `d_viz` | `B_viz = ℝ²` | distance Euclidienne | ≥ 0 |
| `d_score^E` | `B_score = ℝ⁶` | Euclidienne | ≥ 0 |
| `d_score^M` | `B_score` | Mahalanobis pondérée | ≥ 0 |
| `d_w^cos` | simplexe `Δ¹⁰` | dissimilarité cosinus | `[0, 2]` |
| `d_w^JS` | simplexe | Jensen-Shannon | `[0, √ln 2]` |
| `d_w^W` | simplexe | Wasserstein-2 (Sinkhorn) | ≥ 0 |
| `d_T` | tenseurs | Frobenius | ≥ 0 |
| `d_hyb` | combinaison | convexe `(α, β, γ)` | ≥ 0 |

